# Sprint Goal

Design and implement the Research Center as the third major CopyStack product, capable of automatically collecting, analysing, organizing and preserving knowledge that can later be reused by every AI system across the platform.

Unlike the Video Engine, which generates content, and the Outreach Engine, which analyses businesses, the Research Center is responsible for continuously building the platform's long-term intelligence.

---

